# VHS demo — claude-sandbox basic flow

Output docs/demo.webp

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontFamily "JetBrainsMono Nerd Font"
Set Framerate 15
Set CursorBlink false
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 75ms

Hide
Type "cd /Users/iamralch/Projects/github.com/claude-contrib/claude-sandbox && clear"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "echo -n 'Are you running in docker container?' | claude --sandbox"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 25s
